                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "effect": "You unfold the parrying hooks extending from the blade to form a bipod, which has the same benefits as a typical tripod . This negates the \u20132 penalty from kickback but must be reversed by a subsequent Interact action before the weapon can be repositioned or wielded in melee.",
